Daniel is the Nanonauts' singer. He likes to sing a l the time – not just when he's playing with the Nanonauts! His mum and dad say he learned to sing before he learned to talk!
Daniel also plays clarinet and is learning the alto saxophone.
Sam had music in his blood from the day he was born. Both his mum and dad play instruments and got him his first
drum kit when he was only five years old, which led to trouble with the neighbours. On some songs he plays the bass
guitar and on some songs the drums. Sam loves playing in the Nanonauts but hates carrying his drumkit around.
